  "body": "1. as device A, create a group chat with device B\r\n2. as device B, accept the invitation to join a group\r\n3. as device B, leave the group chat \r\n4. as device A, add device B to the same group again\r\n\r\nAs a result, there is no invitation shown for device B to join the group chat\r\n\r\n",
